## Before Generating Code
1. Read the specific module doc: `docs/architecture/modules/{module-name}.md`
2. Verify it follows module boundary rules (`docs/architecture/module-boundaries.md`)
3. Ensure tenant_id is included where required
4. Use the correct naming conventions (`AI_CONTEXT/rules.md`)
5. Check `AI_CONTEXT/known-issues.md` for gotchas
6. For Workforce Intelligence modules: check monitoring toggles + retention policies
